text: BR/BG/RD/RG27520 Research Methods Statistics Practical In the last part of the practical you’ll conduct a statistical test and should enter your results via this quiz link. This is one of eight weekly quizzes that will determine your practical mark for the statistics assignment. As it’s your first quiz, you have unlimited attempts at this one. It must be completed before next Monday’s lecture at the latest, but ideally you should do it today during the practical.
